d is love, and his law, &quot; being an ex-</div><div class="t mb7f x11 he y14c3 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pression of the mind and will of God,&quot; &quot;the transcript of </div><div class="t m333 x11 he y1243 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the character of God,&quot; is founded upon love (Matt. </div><div class="t m14c1 x95 h2b y10e8 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">22 :</div><div class="t m501 xb2 he y10e8 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4o) </div><div class="t mdd8 x11 he y113f ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and fulfilled in love (Rom. 13 : </div><div class="t m5 x2e he y1455 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m5fc x1f he y13b0 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">His commandments </div><div class="t md17 x11 he ydb5 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;are not burdensome&quot; (Matt. </div><div class="t m1552 x80 h2b y1051 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">II </div><div class="t m895 x2a he y1051 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">: 3o) to those who have </div><div class="t m12f0 x11 he y117c ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">been set free from the bondage of sin (John 8: 34-36), but </div><div class="t m157 x11 he y1141 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">rather a delight (Ps. </div><div class="t m37f x39 h2b y15d1 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">I </div><div class="t m1489 x69 he y15d1 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">:2). &quot;The truth a bondage?—Yes, </div><div class="t m7b1 x11 he y986 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">in one sense; it binds the </div><div class="t m6b2 x31 h21 y10f7 ff6 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">willing </div><div class="t mfd x1b he y10f7 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">souls in captivity to Jesus </div><div class="t m69a x11 he y1143 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Christ.&quot; </div><div class="t m13c x18 h2b y1de8 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. VERSES 4, </div><div class="t me7 x10 he y1603 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5.—The greatest victories of the world have </div><div class="t m7bf x11 he y1104 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">been gained through faith (Heb. </div><div class="t m1552 x1b h2b y1104 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">II </div><div class="t m7dd